{"tid":2348883,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"★元旦嬰兒】父母：代表幸運，期望她的誕生，為社會帶來好運","createTime":"2021-01-01T06:09:18.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-02T02:39:17.000Z","uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":84,"uniUserReply":31,"replies":[{"pid":"ca01a57f0d495e4bf294a1986b7c3afc2b71cf9f","tid":2348883,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-01T06:09:18.000Z","msg":"踏入元旦，分別有兩名嬰兒出生。  在仁安醫院，一名女嬰零時零一分順產出世，重3.49公斤，是穆生穆太的第二胎。  <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n對於女兒是「元旦嬰兒」，他們都認為代表幸運，期望她的誕生，為自己、家庭，以至社會帶來好運。父母暫時未想到名字，希望女兒健健康康、過得美好；又指，疫情下每個人都要戴口罩，所以會在家中向她展示多點笑容。  <br />\n<br />\n另一名男嬰零時零分在伊利沙伯醫院順產出生，重3.38公斤。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://news.tvb.com/local/5feeacce335d196617eb0d1a/踏入元旦-本港有一名女嬰及一名男嬰出生\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.tvb.com%2Flocal%2F5feeacce335d196617eb0d1a%2F%E8%B8%8F%E5%85%A5%E5%85%83%E6%97%A6-%E6%9C%AC%E6%B8%AF%E6%9C%89%E4%B8%80%E5%90%8D%E5%A5%B3%E5%AC%B0%E5%8F%8A%E4%B8%80%E5%90%8D%E7%94%B7%E5%AC%B0%E5%87%BA%E7%94%9F&d=h8K6dYNnEA4rSgnLcindhegAExyYYV7WT87CuOwwBqU%3D&h=ec1cdd15\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://news.tvb.com/local/5feeacce335d196617eb0d1a/踏入元旦-本港有一名女嬰及一名男嬰出生</a>"},{"pid":"44b4f2b00545326b906af93041eb2d391deef64b","tid":2348883,"uid":19454,"like":80,"dislike":5,"score":75,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-01T06:09:45.000Z","msg":"完蛋 嬰兒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n一切完蛋"},{"pid":"81716960673ebc7c2d5f6d1daf63f383704130df","tid":2348883,"uid":8038,"like":7,"dislike":1,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-01T06:11:27.000Z","msg":"屌，cctvb"},{"pid":"17a2b896643aa1666585071126d27d04d0af31aa","tid":2348883,"uid":89869,"like":7,"dislike":1,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-01T06:19:13.000Z","msg":"有塊閪冇